    • Method Detail

      • combine

        com.google.common.base.Optional<V> combine(K key,
                                           Iterator<V> updates)
        This function is called to combine the current value of a key with updates that were queued for the key. See the collision free map project level documentation for more information.
        Returns:
        Then new value for the key. Returning Optional.absent() will cause the key to be deleted.
